<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>Eats 메뉴뽑기</title>  
</head>

<body>
<header>
  <% include template/header %>
</header>
<i class="bi bi-list mobile-nav-toggle d-xl-none"></i>
  <header id="header" class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">

  <nav id="navbar" class="navbar nav-menu">
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/" class="nav-link"><i class="bx bx-home"></i> <span>Home</span></a></li>
      <li><a href="/eats" class="nav-link active"><i class="bx bx-server"></i> <span>메뉴뽑기</span></a></li>
      <li><a href="/login" class="nav-link"><i class="bx bx-user"></i> <span>로그인</span></a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>
</header>
<!-- ======= Contact Section ======= -->
<section>
  <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">

    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>1. 위치 찾기</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="row mt-1 mb-5">
      <div class="col-lg-12">
        <!-- 위치 찾기 -->
        <div class="row mb-2">
          <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-12">
                <!-- <span id="postCodeData">현재 위치 정보</span> -->
                <span id="postCodeData"><span>위치 정보 없음</span></span>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-12">
                <button type="button" id="postCodeBtn" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">위치 찾기</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 위치 찾기 종료 -->
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>2. 음식 종류</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="row mt-1 mb-5">
      <div class="col-lg-12">
        <!-- 음식 종류 선택 -->
        <div class="row mb-2">
          <div class="col-sm-12">
            <div class="text-center">
              <p>검색어를 정확하게 입력하지 않을시 데이터가 정확하지 않을 수 있습니다!<br/>ex) 한식, 중식, 일식, 양식, 중식, 파스타, 맛집 등</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <!-- <input type="text" id="keyword"> -->
              <input type="text" id="keyword" placeholder="한식" value="짜장면">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <input type="radio" name="rankby" id="sort1" value="distance" checked>
              <label for="sort1">가까운 곳 기준</label>
              <input type="radio" name="rankby" id="sort2" value="prominence">
              <label for="sort2">인기 있는 곳 기준</label>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" id="foodSearchBtn">음식점 찾기</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 음식 종류 선택 종료 -->
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>3. 결과</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="row mt-1 mb-5">
      <div class="col-lg-12">
        <!-- 결과 맵 -->
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
            <p>결과 리스트</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-1"></div>
          <div class="col-10">
            <div id="map" style="width:100%;height:400px;"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
        <!-- 결과 맵 종료 -->
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- Modal -->
  <div id="modal" class="modal fade" data-bs-backdrop="static" role="dialog">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
      <!-- Modal content-->
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <h4 class="modal-title">뽑기 중</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          <p>검색 결과와 추천 음식점을 뽑는 중입니다. 잠시만 기다려주세요!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- Modal -->
</section>
<footer>
  <% include template/footer %>
</footer>
</body>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
<script src="//t1.daumcdn.net/mapjsapi/bundle/postcode/prod/postcode.v2.js"></script>
<!-- <script type="text/javascript" src="https://openapi.map.naver.com/openapi/v3/maps.js?ncpClientId=<%=process.env.NAVER_CLOUD_ID%>&callback=initNaverMap&submodules=geocoder"></script> -->
<script async defer src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=<%=process.env.GOOGLE_API_KEY%>" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script src="//dapi.kakao.com/v2/maps/sdk.js?appkey=<%=process.env.KAKAO_API_KEY%>&libraries=services"></script>
<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="/js/eats.js"></script>
</html>